{"type":"message","id":"bce0454a","parentId":"eb04780c","timestamp":"2026-03-01T08:09:22.352Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Checking System Status**\n\nI am performing a routine heartbeat check, as requested. The current timestamp is Sunday, March 1st, 2026, 8:09 AM UTC. This process ensures system integrity and responsiveness.\n\n**Performing System Checks**\n\nThe quiet hours have just ended, so I'm moving forward with the scheduled checks. I'm attempting to enforce the Haiku model as per the instructions, though previous attempts to set it have been unsuccessful. I'll then proceed with the email, calendar, weather, and monitoring checks.\n\n**Attempting Model Override**\n\nI'm trying to enforce the Haiku model again, as per the directive. My attempts to set it previously failed, but I'm making one more attempt with `anthropic/claude-haiku`. If this doesn't work, I will note the persistent failure and proceed with the other scheduled checks.\n\n**Executing System Checks**\n\nI am now performing the scheduled system checks as the quiet hours have ended. I've made another attempt to enforce the Haiku model, specifically `anthropic/claude-haiku`, though previous attempts have failed. If this persists, I'll acknowledge the model override failure and proceed with the email, calendar, weather, and monitoring checks, concluding with the `HEARTBEAT_OK` response as no actionable alerts can be determined without specific tools or criteria.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_session_status_cPTqnkmsfxmGPudZSWPg","name":"session_status","arguments":{"model":"anthropic/claude-haiku"},"thoughtSignature":"{\"index\":0,\"id\":\"tool_session_status_cPTqnkmsfxmGPudZSWPg\",\"type\":\"reasoning.encrypted\",\"data\":\"\",\"format\":\"google-gemini-v1\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":15081,"output":1644,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens